/>"},{"pid":"41aa6bb955ee020259fe8f801e48476209113ac6","tid":492423,"uid":52839,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-08T17:53:11.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>沖身先洗頭 熱水一嚟就擔掂落頭到唔好人地講<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n你up乜鳩</blockquote><br />\n解讀：聽人講 熱水一黎就掂到頭唔好"},{"pid":"d69240a56df2b2689d126174670129d5dca8884e","tid":492423,"uid":105302,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-08T17:54:26.000Z","msg":"煤氣爐用家表示除衫個下已經開定水<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"28dfa1048d262139cf8df82092de7434eb9349af","tid":492423,"uid":150033,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-08T17:57:38.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>同樓主一樣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 唔係會覺得好哂水</blockquote><br />\n其實會唔會覺得好寒酸 咁都要慳<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n唔會 啲水白白流走 聽住啲聲好唔心安<br />\n近至多幾蚊水費 遠至諗起好多人冇乾淨水用 <br />\n刷牙都係 刷完先開番水漱口"},{"pid":"d7bbd39deb43e8ce3f110e0310b9ca0ae4038c7e","tid":492423,"uid":151774,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-08T18:00:11.000Z","msg":"我得十秒沖涼，仲要有個人係我後面數住"},{"pid":"188b4ff4e574154f322588f3794ce54f47bb8145","tid":492423,"uid":14103,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-08T18:06:36.000Z","msg":"我用煤氣, 完全唔知你地咩感覺<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"15abfbef5003dadd6d19c003cbdf7cc809197882","tid":492423,"uid":44917,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-08T18:11:40.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>先洗頭但唔冲身，成頭泡果時再冲身揸沐浴露，之後花灑向頭淋，一次過冲走頭泡同身果d泡<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n巴打冬天你點算 硬漢子<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"013c595cafe5045e65a1f95db67ad63ae6265630","tid":492423,"uid":65530,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-08T18:15:27.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"730d821a38d1ee35ecac9bac9ab5df1a7786a75a","tid":492423,"uid":11629,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-08T18:17:04.000Z","msg":"煤氣爐<br />\n洗頭：將個頭移離水位再搽洗頭水，個身一直淋住水<br />\n洗身：向前踏一步再9秒9搽匀全身番梘再淋返水<br />\n屋企個爐一閂左熱水個爐就自動熄<br />\n之後開返又等幾秒先有返熱水<br />\n變相好似更嘥水<br />\n同埋短時間内開閂感覺好似容易壞d"},{"pid":"0482fa9f2e3937e21d05168d2ca9f315630f786f","tid":492423,"uid":55628,"like":0,"dislike":7,"score":-7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-08T18:24:10.000Z","msg":"沖你老母涼液咩？沐浴露就沐浴露啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"689534ccc12a18121eb19814401bbe41bba666c1","tid":492423,"uid":120955,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-08T18:24:43.000Z","msg":"由頭到尾開住煤氣爐淋<br />\n一開波用10分鐘思考人生<br />\n到咁上下煙霧瀰漫就搽野<br />\n再用10分鐘沖身刷牙洗面痾尿"},{"pid":"036beffba1a7fac496e785b4907732fe92188d7b","tid":492423,"uid":71373,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-08T18:26:05.000Z","msg":"早幾年仲可以冬天沖凍水涼<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n依加唔得"},{"pid":"45208bf0ccb7c8107e2fa4ef42058eeb95e48ec2","tid":492423,"uid":80443,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-08T18:27:55.000Z","msg":"儲水式<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/fozen_smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n冬天要開幾分鐘熱水焗暖浴室然後熄水嗱嗱臨搽洗頭水，沖沖手上啲泡順手搽埋梘液<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/fozen_smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />再開返熱水沖<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/fozen_smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />啲水唔夠十五分鐘就開始凍<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/fozen_smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/fozen_smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c6ecda35cf47adcdf1698a8c126dd74137785b50","tid":492423,"uid":44917,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-08T18:35:57.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>沖你老母涼液咩？沐浴露就沐浴露啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\