c=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n好似有啲浪費<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"99a9db24ed8ad50b220570b66b4bfcd8db4a8e87","tid":492423,"uid":44917,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-08T18:53:09.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>沖身先洗頭 熱水一嚟就擔掂落頭到唔好人地講<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n你up乜鳩</blockquote><br />\n解讀：聽人講 熱水一黎就掂到頭唔好</blockquote><br />\nagger<br />\n不過沖一陣嗰身先沖頭又得姐"},{"pid":"bab8a9331d6aefe47a4b1595b1cd97ce243deb58","tid":492423,"uid":55594,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-08T18:55:16.000Z","msg":"屋企煤氣爐開要load 5-10秒先變恆溫 所以唔會重開<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"df4a8e12f1b5de3cafa819c481b3e3b52d2b919d","tid":492423,"uid":55594,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-08T18:55:16.000Z","msg":"屋企煤氣爐開要load 5-10秒先變恆溫 所以唔會重開<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"522da4cfa7117d2587fa4e99f12ce5bec9e3ef25","tid":492423,"uid":148011,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-08T19:03:25.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>即熱式。<br />\n會淋住搽<br />\n習慣先用洗頭水然後沖水 跟住搽護髮素但唔沖水住 跟住洗面同身 最後先沖護髮素 好似短暫焗油咁</blockquote><br />\n咁樣最後先沖，啲護髮素咪沖晒落身度，護髮素好難洗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我平時用完護髮素過完水先用沖涼液，就係為咗洗走身上面啲痴住既護髮素<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n利申，勁長頭髮，易皮膚敏感<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6ac00d6140a01083acc9a71bb3a6e292687c4b1d","tid":492423,"uid":24160,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-08T19:05:20.000Z","msg":"係洗頭渣洗頭水同護髮素先開住"},{"pid":"6b36fbb981f817dd01170610c88b70c837d19da1","tid":492423,"uid":80461,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-08T19:11:06.000Z","msg":"儲水式<br />\n<br />\n會熄水，但唔關係咪儲水定即熱式事<br />\n習慣問題<br />\nbtw 個爐得18L但次次都用唔曬"},{"pid":"f15c71fa62b38bfd699c7408aeae01abddcda3c9","tid":492423,"uid":29485,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-08T19:24:01.000Z","msg":"搭單問 由細到大都係用即熱or煤氣<br />\n黎緊搬去村屋 要用儲水式<br />\n想問d熱水通常last到幾耐<br />\n<br />\n利伸 冬天夏天都係沖一個鐘涼<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6e87c4e28d70d259ab05c7c8a6abdbdfc2591286","tid":492423,"uid":103983,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-08T19:28:18.000Z","msg":"有冇人沖緊涼同我一樣會突然斷片<br />\n唔記得有冇落洗頭水<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3296a7ae9c43866b55d510ec38732ea32436deab","tid":492423,"uid":17052,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-08T19:41:19.000Z","msg":"即熱 會熄<br />\n冬天都熄"},{"pid":"adaea6c0549f24d6f15d61c77038745055dd91eb","tid":492423,"uid":162344,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-08T19:43:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f0883538d7ceafe806f692e4db8e80c55cbc4eef","tid":492423,"uid":27830,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-08T19:45:37.000Z","msg":"沖住點搽梘<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3ebd576d29609ad00a71980ce68890761810ceab","tid":492423,"uid":44917,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-08T19:53:38.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>沖住點搽梘<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n好多因素：<br />\n沖涼位面積<br />\n咩類型熱水爐<br />\n仲有 你同我都唔知嘅嘢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"689b89525cb1bac03cef0da0df4b0387590d0ceb","tid":492423,"uid":44917,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-08T19:54:01.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>即熱 會熄<br />\n冬天都熄</blockquote><br />\n環保哥<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0cbb79ffd7854090f583577ee13d74476d83ec6f","tid":492423,"uid":44917,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-08T19:54:42.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>有冇人沖緊涼同我一樣會突然斷片<br />\n唔記得有冇落洗頭水<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n去check check個人好啲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a05dfe691a4593b8cc9b850b223855e2fba54b7d","tid":492423,"uid":27403,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-08T20:27:37.000Z","msg":"煤氣恆溫<br />\n會熄水<br />\n因為有超撚嘥電嘅暖風機<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f04e3b5c2477842b8dbe51259fd6cf09c7827910","tid":492423,"uid":122680,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-08T21:14:50.000Z","msg":"而家用煤氣爐沖，一年4季會長開，就算搽洗頭水或沐浴露，都唔會熄水<br />\n<br />\n以前用儲水式，冬天沖涼得果5分鐘有夠暖身體既熱水，沖涼次序就係：<br />\n1）先開熱水淋頭<br />\n2）熄水<br />\n3）用洗頭水<br />\n4）開熱水沖頭同濕全身<br />\n5）熄水<br />\n6）搽護髮素同沐浴露<br />\n7）開熱水沖乾全身，直至熱水用完<br />\n<br />\n開得太熱或開得太大水，都會令到有熱水既時間縮少<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"773a8bca83a6a1497083373d69ae7e6beaeaf743","tid":492423,"uid":64716,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-08T21:51:15.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>用緊儲水式電熱水爐<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/16.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n花灑一定關 唔係唔夠熱水用<br />\n沖到最尾會凍到pk <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n之前住hall個到用即熱式<br />\n可能因為平時關慣<br />\n所以都會關左花灑先搽沖涼液同洗頭水<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n其實我真係唔撚明，點解今時今日仲要用儲水式，真係揾自己笨。"},{"pid":"99786be7dbb9ace68adf601e71ea92e53a58281b","tid":492423,"uid":64716,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-08T21:57:43.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>其實儲水式唔可以開住個爐沖咩？</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n最盡得個3000w , 根本冇可能回到氣。<br />\n至於即熱式只有某些高級笨柒豪宅先會裝到，因為洗手minimum都6~7kw ,沖涼至少18kw ,必需3相供電，一般大廈或家居何來3相電源？ 就算單相7kw也難以提供。"},{"pid":"9e19772def2371c5240083815f98338cc5241558","tid":492423,"uid":64716,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-08T22:10:13.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>儲水式<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/fozen_smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n冬天要開幾分鐘熱水焗暖浴室然後熄水嗱嗱臨搽洗頭水，沖沖手上啲泡順手搽埋梘液<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/fozen_smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />再開返熱水沖<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/fozen_smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />啲水唔夠十五分鐘就開始凍<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/fozen_smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/fozen_smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n以前細個 得個o的 16升儲水，最凍10度以下實際得返7分鐘左右，最慘所有儲水式都係一路用係一路凍水入，即係溫度一路下降，變相你要不斷加大熱水量去平衡個溫度。<br />\n舊式公屋廁所個氣窗仲要係百葉窗對街，根本漏風，係個5至7分鐘內你要安全出返黎簡直係神技。 當然計埋中間熄水回氣，補返30秒血完成任務啦。<br />\n<br />\n到自己出身有自己屋後，我再未用過儲水式，之前林內牌o的濕鳩氣爐冬天夠哂熱但夏天真係人都煲熟埋，後來换左個電子衡溫爽到而家。"},{"pid":"8e8d42e1ee304a5741067b79a39a50b1f0855fe8","tid":492423,"uid":64716,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-08T22:12:46.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>搭單問 由細到大都係用即熱or煤氣<br />\n黎緊搬去村屋 要用儲水式<br />\n想問d熱水通常last到幾耐<br />\n<br />\n利伸 冬天夏天都係沖一個鐘涼<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n關咩事， 村屋一樣可以用石油氣。<br />\npan記同多田牌有石油氣用，平o的就德國寶。"},{"pid":"3ab21f478ccfde215a17e1411b318513dedc64b6","tid":492423,"uid":64716,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-08T22:18:45.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>煤氣恆溫<br />\n會熄水<br />\n因為有超撚嘥電嘅暖風機<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n咁撚仆街o既？？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n同我一樣廁所有澡室寶。。<br />\n同埋小至型冷氣扇<br />\n<br />\n人一世物一世， 其他野我可以放棄追求，但煲廁所個段時間係relax同享受， 去少次旅行，出少幾次街食飯省返黎個buget都夠做。"},{"pid":"b2178d38dd2efcc2d2ccd464b1346ebfd8880daf","tid":492423,"uid":86988,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-08T22:19:56.000Z","msg":"即熱煤氣爐<br />\n沖水-&gt;淨沖身-&gt;搽洗頭水+洗面乳-&gt;沖頭-&gt;較細水-&gt;搽沖涼液-&gt;沖身-&gt;完<br />\n上面嗰個係慢嘅大概5分鐘<br />\n快嘅就大概1分鐘(全身都用沖涼液)<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"53cee30dcb7395474572f0f86a677a7b057b0eaf","tid":492423,"uid":86988,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-08T22:20:38.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>即熱煤氣爐<br />\n沖水-&gt;淨沖身-&gt;搽洗頭水+洗面乳-&gt;沖頭-&gt;較細水-&gt;搽沖涼液-&gt;沖身-&gt;完<br />\n上面嗰個係慢嘅大概5分鐘<br />\n快嘅就大概1分鐘(全身都用沖涼液)<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n利申:企浴"},{"pid":"38c409400f19ff40df6a4cb4c9203820bedf9768","tid":492423,"uid":86988,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-08T22:23:05.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>煤氣恆溫<br />\n會熄水<br />\n因為有<span style=\"color: red;\">超撚嘥電嘅暖風機</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n乾撚到仆街<br />\n利申：皮膚好敏感，好似乾/濕到痕"},{"pid":"9e9e0bba4e14372f74fc3658707a6c30d4c3914c","tid":492423,"uid":3399,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-08T23:34:14.000Z","msg":"儲水式，唔關水，關咗又要再較水，開住水仲有啲熱氣噴過黎無咁凍<br />\n<br />\n唔明點解啲人話儲水要極快沖完，我一直沖涼都沖好耐，沖到最尾啲水都仲暖<br />\n<br />\n究竟你地係熄咗電先沖定係開好大水，我用加壓花灑唔洗開好大"},{"pid":"40a7a86764952e4df2dd559ebe271a211f6a3f25","tid":492423,"uid":3399,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-08T23:38:56.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>用緊儲水式電熱水爐<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/16.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n花灑一定關 唔係唔夠熱水用<br />\n沖到最尾會凍到pk <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n之前住hall個到用即熱式<br />\n可能因為平時關慣<br />\n所以都會關左花灑先搽沖涼液同洗頭水<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n其實我真係唔撚明，點解今時今日仲要用儲水式，真係揾自己笨。</blockquote><br />\n舊式唐樓邊有煤氣，連沖廁都要用食水<br />\n你試下租間房黎住先啦，我都唔想咁搵笨嫁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e7df255e739816720d5ee068459b0806f5d035d7","tid":492423,"uid":10221,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-08T23:43:40.000Z","msg":"儲水式<br />\n<br />\n平時一定係沖完身先洗頭"},{"pid":"7946c899d23ae14dc3ed5940b0dffd7e86a62508","tid":492423,"uid":68848,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-08T23:54:51.000Z","msg":"會<br />\n利申： 仲沖緊凍水涼"},{"pid":"a646bad324fbb93a615d153a395c69084a2f2202","tid":492423,"uid":108756,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-09T00:25:21.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>其實儲水式唔可以開住個爐沖咩？</blockquote><br />\n好似話會無哂啲熱水 我都未用過唔知"},{"pid":"f3fec118c7eb181bd494856f35810ee465f6320b","tid":492423,"uid":55458,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-09T00:49:12.000Z","msg":"沖個涼都寒酸到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3acfc7b506930e3a95ab938469a273962bf6b3cb","tid":492423,"uid":85243,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-09T00:54:59.000Z","msg":"即熱爐<br />\n唔開水, 要捽上身果陣就用對腳夾住花灑暖住下身<br />\n到要捽下身就掛起花灑(呢個時間只會淋到背脊同pat)<br />\n然後曲起隻腳洗成條腿同腳板<br />\n最後蹲低洗下面同埋菊花"},{"pid":"ee1731b0a43221c85cca8daf46416ab186218a08","tid":492423,"uid":85243,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-09T00:55:29.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>即熱爐<br />\n唔<span style=\"color: red;\">關</span>水, 要捽上身果陣就用對腳夾住花灑暖住下身<br />\n到要捽下身就掛起花灑(呢個時間只會淋到背脊同pat)<br />\n然後曲起隻腳洗成條腿同腳板<br />\n最後蹲低洗下面同埋菊花</blockquote>"},{"pid":"9d702ed5af459762ad9e70e61cd1e754187151e3","tid":492423,"uid":28279,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-09T01:18:40.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 你哋係咪唔洗腳板底？"},{"pid":"2f6e551951300222d384fe9aa9491a3ef9fb138f","tid":492423,"uid":32380,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-09T01:51:25.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>由入去果刻開水開到出嚟果秒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n成日比人話晒水<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 一年四季都係咁</blockquote><br />\n你全程沖幾耐先<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n大約15分鐘啫</blockquote><br />\n同我一樣WO<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n一齊沖啦我地<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"36e874ad44192d6c3a67e940f6c0710190a9edb3","tid":492423,"uid":44917,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-09T02:22:04.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>搭單問 由細到大都係用即熱or煤氣<br />\n黎緊搬去村屋 要用儲水式<br />\n想問d熱水通常last到幾耐<br />\n<br />\n利伸 冬天夏天都係沖一個鐘涼<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n關咩事， 村屋一樣可以用石油氣。<br />\npan記同多田牌有石油氣用，平o的就德國寶。</blockquote><br />\n洗頭沖涼點做到一個鐘<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"66c90222257baaa2b02778b22d37286a23b4408b","tid":492423,"uid":44917,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-09T02:25:01.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>即熱爐<br />\n唔開水, 要捽上身果陣就用對腳夾住花灑暖住下身<br />\n到要捽下身就掛起花灑(呢個時間只會淋到背脊同pat)<br />\n然後曲起隻腳洗成條腿同腳板<br />\n最後蹲低洗下面同埋菊花</blockquote><br />\n幾好喎 應該好快搞掂"},{"pid":"4d34a4f89278f982b085ae315d7cc4fa5d912e34","tid":492423,"uid":98507,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-09T03:16:47.000Z","msg":"搽洗頭水定淋浴露都會熄野<br />\n窮撚慳得就慳<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"81c4890e2073e64d487529e06a2d47d64e0a85b7","tid":492423,"uid":4635,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-09T03:40:09.000Z","msg":"儲水式另外一個仆街地方就要開定先<br />\n有時一返到屋企或者第二朝起身想即刻沖個涼都唔得<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8accff32bbb051c4b757a3f8742a73bdbb9044aa","tid":492423,"uid":15336,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-09T04:14:14.000Z","msg":"淋住身查洗頭水<br />\n淋住背脊捽正面身<br />\n淋住正面身捽背脊"}]}